 would never forgive him in a million years!"],[7732,7803,"No way."],[7995,8070,"So... what were you gonna say?"]],"44":[[41,137,"It's..."],[300,379,"it's..."],[550,654,"Actually, never mind."],[725,855,"Okay, okay."],[855,971,"What's going on?"],[971,1113,"You two are acting weird."],[1238,1409,"Is there some sort of secret?"],[1564,1618,"Um..."],[1710,1789,"I..."],[2047,2139,"I have a boyfriend!"],[2323,2423,"Emma!"],[2423,2619,"That's amazing! That's such great news!"],[2619,2798,"Why didn't you just say it sooner?"],[2815,2986,"I was worried I wouldn't have enough time"],[2986,3128,"for you and Dad anymore."],[3128,3228,"Hmm..."],[3345,3445,"Don't worry about that."],[3445,3586,"We will look out for each other."],[3670,3732,"Now..."],[3732,3995,"let's cheers to Emma and her new boyfriend!"],[3995,4275,"Cheers to Emma and her new boyfriend!"],[5030,5221,"I can't believe Jennifer..."],[5292,5497,"hated that undercover billionaire so much."],[5547,5593,"Dad,"],[5647,5751,"what should we do now?"],[5855,5951,"I guess..."],[6035,6222,"We're stuck pretending to be poor."],[6348,6481,"Let's just hope we don't slip up."],[6840,6923,"Aye, aye, captain."],[7365,7590,"Jennifer, could you help me write this card?"],[7653,7736,"Why do you need me to check it?"],[7791,7891,"I have dyslexia."],[7937,8116,"You... you have dyslexia, too?"]],"45":[[0,158,"Wait, you too?"],[196,450,"No, my... lost daughter."],[1155,1509,"I guess we're more alike than I thought."],[1722,1889,"Yes. There was a “Congratulations”"],[1889,1972,"that isn't right."],[1972,2181,"My girl couldn't nail that one down either."],[2306,2456,"Here, let me write it down for you."],[2840,2927,"That writing!"],[3653,3778,"Oh, look at that."],[3778,3966,"My girl's a natural!"],[4229,4396,"The exact same handwriting!"],[4421,4471,"Is..."],[4554,4658,"Jennifer..."],[4658,4808,"my mom?"],[4934,4992,"Uh..."],[4992,5055,"What's wrong?"]],"46":[[0,137,"Uh... What's wrong?"],[646,850,"Nothing. I was just overthinking."],[1317,1564,"This mole has a risk of becoming cancerous."],[1626,1805,"It's better to get it removed soon."],[1805,2022,"Okay, alright. Let's do it now."],[2093,2206,"Emma, let's go."],[2273,2427,"I'll drop you off on the way to work."],[2515,2594,"I'll miss you."],[2748,2815,"See you tonight."],[3628,3816,"Oh, my forgetful husband,"],[3816,3974,"forgot his truck keys."],[4124,4229,"Paul, you for..."],[4421,4517,"A Rolls-Royce?"],[4517,4667,"You have been lying to me?!"]],"47":[[45,191,"You have been lying to me?!"],[304,508,"This is all so strange!"],[1222,1372,"You're all top executives"],[1372,1540,"on the L.A. billionaire list."],[1609,1714,"It's an honor to discuss"],[1714,1922,"potential collaborations with you today."],[2239,2339,"Paul?"],[2481,2706,"Ma'am, you must be confused."],[2706,2823,"This is a private,"],[2823,2957,"high-end gathering."],[2957,3249,"Paul, why aren't you at work? And..."],[3332,3432,"Why the..."],[3432,3516,"fancy suit,"],[3516,3611,"and this place?"],[3611,3737,"The car? And..."],[3737,3820,"you."],[3820,3912,"What are you doing here?"],[3970,4133,"Actually... this is a reunion"],[4133,4262,"for my Dad's Navy friends!"],[4262,4316,"Yes!"],[4362,4462,"That's it, exactly."],[4500,4571,"Really?"],[4571,4646,"Hmm."],[4854,5134,"I heard Paul is hiding his identity to woo his wife."],[5234,5359,"I can't screw this up for them."],[5555,5622,"Hi!"],[5622,5747,"My name's James."],[5747,5968,"I was in the logistics division in the military."],[6018,6206,"Now I run a luxury car rental company."],[6256,6427,"I'm the one who drove Paul here"],[6427,6527,"in the fancy car."],[6619,6777,"Well, thank you for"],[6777,7019,"taking care of Paul all these years."],[7052,7215,"Well, we'll be counting on Paul to..."],[7257,7399,"take care of us in the future!"],[7482,7570,"Of course."],[7570,7761,"Hey, I'm Mike, the medic!"],[7799,7895,"And I'm Jack,"],[7974,8041,"the mechanic!"],[8137,8387,"If this keeps going, we're gonna be exposed..."],[8500,8658,"Paul, I'm so sorry."],[8658,8787,"You're just trying to go out"],[8787,8888,"and meet your friends,"],[8888,9038,"and I just... I doubted you."],[9084,9200,"Don't say that. It's my fault."]],"48":[[0,125,"Don't say that. It's my fault."],[125,283,"No. Really, it's just..."],[367,442,"I shouldn't have come."],[596,711,"This is a happy event!"],[767,880,"Don't apologize!"],[1017,1096,"Let's drink together!"],[1116,1263,"—Here we go. —Thank you."],[1551,1626,"Cheers!"],[2285,2460,"Oh, thank you so much!"],[2665,2886,"Oh, wow! A shooting star!"],[3015,3232,"Oh, I wish our family to be happy forever!"],[3524,3620,"You know what?"],[3620,3682,"Wait."],[3724,3807,"You're the one that's always"],[3807,3949,"making my wishes come true."],[3983,4216,"I wish to be with you forever!"],[4341,4400,"Jennifer,"],[4512,4617,"I know how you feel about lying."],[4733,4842,"If I lied to you..."],[4842,5021,"What did you do to upset me?"],[5067,5159,"I, um..."],[5159,5201,"You know what?"],[5201,5317,"It doesn't even matter because"],[5317,5409,"no matter what you did,"],[5409,5518,"you'll always have a chance"],[5518,5619,"to be forgiven by me."],[5747,5876,"Well, in that case,"],[6001,6131,"I want to come clean."],[6373,6506,"I'm a billionaire."],[6664,6790,"I'm Paul Marshall."]],"49":[[125,233,"I'm a billionaire."],[425,538,"I'm Paul Marshall."],[2118,2318,"I'll tell her everything once she wakes up."],[3319,3428,"Thank you."],[3482,3570,"I'm glad you're here."],[3636,3749,"Any chance I can get a reward?"],[3803,3920,"Oh? Like what?"],[3995,4154,"Like a hot, passionate night."],[4633,4842,"Consider that your down payment."],[5040,5170,"Jenn, do you remember"],[5170,5271,"what you said to me last night?"],[5426,5605,"I don't know. I did drink a lot last night."],[5755,5989,"You said that we'd always be together as a family,"],[5989,6076,"forever."],[6110,6331,"Right, yeah. I think I remember that now."],[6347,6481,"And that if I ever lied to you,"],[6481,6648,"you'd at least forgive me once."],[6702,6894,"Okay, what'd you lie to me about?"],[7094,7173,"I'm ready now."],[7261,7340,"Okay,"],[7340,7436,"the truth is..."],[7582,7628,"I'm..."]],"50":[[16,100,"The truth is..."],[208,237,"I'm..."],[237,275,"Paul!"],[367,531,"We need a cleanup on 906."],[531,613,"Get to work!"],[1343,1526,"So, you're just a supermarket worker?"],[1633,1841,"How could Paul ever be interested"],[1841,2047,"in someone like you?"],[2047,2264,"I earn my money through hard work,"],[2264,2489,"unlike you, through vanity and greed!"],[2489,2663,"You are just a parasite!"],[2727,2815,"Bitch!"],[2815,3044,"You're only with Paul for his cash,"],[3044,3111,"admit it!"],[3111,3265,"At least I'm not like you,"],[3265,3357,"gold-digger!"],[3695,3841,"Paul may be just a truck driver,"],[3841,4045,"but he's an honest, hardworking man."],[4087,4358,"And he is so far out of your league."],[4358,4496,"Paul Marshall?"],[4496,4604,"A truck driver?"],[4671,4800,"Has he never told you?"],[4859,5025,"He's L.A.'s wealthiest man,"],[5084,5196,"Paul Marshall!"],[5455,5534,"Damn it!"]],"51":[[204,404,"She doesn't even know you're a billionaire!"],[404,581,"Seems like you don't trust her at all."],[646,863,"You are just a lying snake."],[863,1005,"Leave now!"],[1005,1109,"Get out of my way!"],[1146,1393,"I've come for my man and you're not stopping me."],[1393,1622,"Paul and I, we made a vow before God."],[1622,1830,"Rich as a Rockefeller or broke as a bum."],[1830,1943,"He is mine."],[1943,2220,"And you will never tear us apart in this lifetime!"],[2364,2494,"Oh, please!"],[2494,2681,"This big talk only means that"],[2681,2940,"you are too scared to lose your price catch!"],[3607,3732,"Jennifer doesn't need to lie."],[3841,4004,"Everything I have belongs to her."],[4154,4212,"Paul..."],[4212,4433,"I'm slapping a restraining order on you."],[4433,4496,"Get lost."],[5117,5217,"I'm so sorry, Jenn."],[5284,5376,"I lied to you."],[5376,5476,"Can you forgive me?"],[5526,5659,"Forgive you for what?"],[5793,5943,"I hid my billionaire identity."],[6106,6277,"You said that you'd always forgive me once."],[6277,6381,"Does this still count?"],[6573,6627,"Paul,"],[6627,6752,"your ex-wife is gone."],[6752,6973,"You don't need to keep playing pretend with me."],[7111,7186,"What?"],[7186,7403,"I really do appreciate your humor."],[7474,7603,"I'm getting back to work."],[7862,7999,"But I really am a billionaire!"],[8829,8904,"Jennifer,"],[8904,9000,"we need to come clean."],[9071,9121,"He..."],[9121,9263,"really is the owner of..."],[9263,9417,"the PM Group. And..."],[9417,9542,"I'm the CFO."],[9597,9788,"So Paul, everything you said to me before"],[9788,9876,"was true?"],[9955,10080,"Absolutely true!"],[10164,10251,"Well,"],[10251,10489,"I've been hiding my true identity as well."],[10627,10702,"What?"]],"52":[[196,479,"Jennifer, representing Cincinnati, Ohio,"],[533,734,"hailing from the good old U.S.A.!"],[763,871,"And, drumroll,"],[905,1013,"I'm your Miss World pageant champ!"],[1055,1101,"Wait, what?"],[1167,1222,"Seriously?!"],[1526,1614,"April Fool's!"],[1735,1958,"Nice try, but you guys aren't fooling me!"],[2435,2573,"What are we gonna do now?"],[2656,2823,"I mean, I never thought it would end up like this!"],[2944,3086,"How about we..."],[3086,3228,"skip the talk and show her?"],[3361,3411,"How?"],[3461,3624,"We can take her on our private jet"],[3624,3728,"to a private island!"],[3795,4024,"We'll get her jewelry, a mansion, a yacht!"],[4108,4275,"It's a little over the top, but..."],[4362,4466,"I think it could work."],[4466,4558,"Aye, aye, boss man!"],[5793,5897,"Daniel,"],[5897,6026,"how nice of you to call."],[6101,6151,"What's up?"],[6206,6264,"Mom,"],[6314,6562,"I'm outside on the street. I need your help!"]],"53":[[654,709,"Daniel,"],[792,888,"what happened to you?!"],[1096,1230,"After..."],[1230,1334,"Dad went bankrupt,"],[1384,1520,"Rebecca divorced me,"],[1520,1612,"took all my money"],[1612,1738,"and kicked me out of the house."],[1847,1992,"You dug this hole yourself."],[2164,2378,"I've always wanted to repay Mom's money."],[2378,2705,"I'd saved up $20,000, but Rebecca took that too."],[2802,2998,"Paul already got the money back for me."],[2998,3199,"What stung was how you treated us,"],[3199,3403,"like dirt beneath your shoe."],[3478,3657,"Mom, I hate myself for it."],[4225,4400,"I took all your life savings!"],[4400,4562,"I made you homeless!"],[4562,4767,"No wonder you ended up with a male stripper..."],[5288,5388,"Enough, Daniel."],[5505,5593,"I forgive you."],[5684,5864,"No mother can hold a grudge against"],[5864,5943,"her kid forever."],[6252,6343,"I'm sorry."],[6911,6994,"Can you help him?"],[6994,7073,"Well..."],[7102,7251,"Since it's you that's asking..."],[7419,7465,"Daniel,"],[7528,7615,"you'll have to step up—"],[7711,7853,"prove that you got your mom's back"],[7853,7932,"the way that I do."],[7995,8113,"Then we'll be square."],[8208,8313,"Exactly."],[8354,8441,"I promise!"],[8533,8700,"I'll get a new job"],[8700,8872,"and move out as soon as possible!"],[8992,9059,"Actually,"],[9250,9405,"I think you should come work at PM Group."],[9584,9718,"You make it sound like the PM Group"],[9718,9884,"is your family business."],[10089,10172,"Kind of is!"],[10310,10410,"You two and your jokes."],[10410,10681,"You just... just love kidding around."],[11232,11315,"Hey, Daniel."],[11340,11561,"Mom! I really got the job at PM Group!"],[11611,11787,"I think it was the chairman himself"],[11787,11899,"who arranged it for me!"],[11952,12010,"Wait."],[12010,12303,"So, Paul really is the CEO of the PM Group?!"]],"54":[[62,266,"Impossible, Mom. Paul's just a driver."],[354,575,"Maybe the chairman has heard of me before?"],[625,709,"Yeah, could be."],[763,934,"After all, you're a talented young man."],[992,1091,"This is a fresh start."],[1142,1217,"I'll work hard now, Mom."],[1284,1334,"Good."],[1409,1488,"Bye, honey."],[2235,2365,"Listen up, losers."],[2410,2605,"I'm interviewing for the supervisor position."],[2640,2852,"Obviously, I'll be getting it soon."],[2852,3055,"So, you'd all better be nice to me!"],[3582,3657,"Hey, you!"],[3657,3770,"Go get me a coffee!"],[3978,4083,"You?"],[4083,4187,"You, scum?"],[4187,4341,"What the hell are you doing here?"],[4341,4446,"I work here."],[4446,4658,"Bullshit! A loser like you working at PM Group?!"],[4825,4925,"Get out of here!"],[4988,5146,"You have no right to tell me what to do."],[5405,5587,"You and your mother are both scum!"],[5587,5755,"Don't you dare insult my mom!"],[5755,5880,"She's the best person in the world,"],[5880,5972,"and you're the trash here!"],[6043,6181,"I'll smash your damn head! Dan..."],[6181,6247,"Enough!"]],"55":[[12,70,"You?"],[125,241,"Jennifer's husband?!"],[342,500,"Nobody makes a scene in my company."],[500,583,"Your company?!"],[633,742,"You fool,"],[742,909,"quit acting like a big shot!"],[909,1048,"I'm about to be the boss here!"],[1263,1409,"Son of a bitch!"],[1409,1622,"The chairman asked to meet with me!"],[1622,1755,"You'll regret this!"],[1910,2072,"Do you wanna guess who the chairman is?"],[2072,2369,"Whoever it is, it's not an old fart like you!"],[2369,2544,"Let's show her who the real chairman is!"],[3465,3613,"Good morning, Chairman Paul!"],[3695,3774,"You?"],[4041,4108,"You?"],[4237,4396,"What, you thought you could just waltz in here"],[4396,4464,"for an interview?"],[4521,4725,"We called you to cough up what you owe Daniel!"],[4725,4821,"And what if I don't?!"],[4913,5092,"How about a full industry blacklist"],[5142,5292,"and a one-way ticket to prison?"],[5509,5676,"Daniel, I'm sorry!"],[5676,5755,"I'll pay you back."],[5755,5830,"I promise."],[5901,6022,"Here's my card."],[6172,6315,"Save it, you scared little rat!"],[6352,6423,"We're done!"],[6473,6531,"Daniel!"],[6569,6678,"I'm sorry about your mom."],[6678,6802,"We will get back together!"],[6802,6886,"We're done!"],[6936,7002,"Let's show her what it's like"],[7002,7091,"to get kicked out!"],[7157,7240,"Security!"],[7766,7845,"Daniel!"],[8721,8780,"Seems like you"],[8780,8929,"hate the PM Group just like I do."],[9188,9309,"Wanna get revenge together?"],[9943,10118,"I saw you defend your mom's honor there."],[10214,10293,"Well done."],[10364,10489,"I should have done it a long time ago."],[10652,10819,"So, you really are the billionaire."],[11027,11219,"I'm gonna call my mom and tell her the truth."]],"56":[[141,262,"I plan on telling her everything"],[262,371,"at her birthday party."],[675,834,"Mom hit the jackpot meeting you two."],[1067,1146,"I know."],[1918,1997,"Paul,"],[2077,2293,"thank you for making all my wishes come true."],[2802,3028,"I only wish that we could find your daughter."],[3148,3282,"You've given me hope, though."],[3328,3503,"You made me believe that we will..."],[3503,3586,"find her one day."],[4045,4138,"Plus, you have made"],[4138,4295,"all my other wishes come true."],[6539,6660,"Happy birthday, my darling."],[6715,6856,"Enjoy these appetizers."],[6927,7090,"More surprises await you today."],[8837,8958,"Jennifer?"],[9300,9409,"What are you guys doing here?"],[9609,9713,"Is that Paul?"]],"57":[[0,171,"Hey, Dad. You wanna go grab some lunch?"],[171,250,"Sure."],[633,675,"Yeah."],[675,800,"Hey, Mr. Marshall."],[800,892,"Your wife's in my hands."],[892,1030,"I want 20 million in ransom!"],[1030,1163,"If you try to call the cops,"],[1163,1309,"she's as good as dead."],[1309,1409,"You..."],[1409,1555,"kidnapped Jennifer?"],[1639,1764,"Trace the call."],[1826,1922,"Hello, FBI?"],[2010,2091,"We need the phone location"],[2091,2260,"of the person talking to Mr. Marshall."],[2260,2348,"We're locking it in."],[2348,2485,"Please keep the line open."],[2540,2635,"Buy time!"],[2806,2898,"Let me hear her voice."],[3165,3328,"Paul, it's Rebecca and Ali—"],[3357,3457,"Shut up, bitch!"],[3457,3507,"Stop!"],[3507,3703,"If you lay a hand on her, you'll lose everything!"],[3782,3949,"I'm giving you ten minutes."],[3949,4079,"Send the money to this account."],[4079,4179,"That's too rushed."],[4179,4258,"Give me an hour."],[4258,4346,"Thirty minutes."],[4346,4550,"A second late, and you'll start preparing her body!"],[5005,5113,"We've got the location!"]],"58":[[321,392,"Hang on!"],[392,499,"I'm coming, Jennifer!"],[921,1105,"Rebecca, don't throw your life away!"],[1105,1263,"This is kidnapping and extortion!"],[1380,1564,"Bitch! I've already lost everything!"],[1564,1685,"It's all your fault!"],[1685,1750,"Damn right!"],[1785,1960,"Let's grab our torture tools."],[2406,2485,"Rebecca,"],[2485,2577,"let me go!"],[2577,2696,"You used to be my son's wife."],[2696,2824,"I will forgive you. Just please."],[2824,2936,"Please, let me go!"],[2965,3048,"I'm gonna end you!"],[3211,3282,"Right now!"],[3511,3570,"Jennifer!"],[3632,3712,"Paul!"],[3712,3787,"Emma!"],[3895,4016,"Paul, please!"],[4016,4124,"Don't do this to me!"],[4124,4283,"Emma, stop Rebecca!"],[4300,4505,"Let go of me or I'll kill her!"],[4537,4604,"Dad,"],[4604,4683,"I can't."],[4758,4826,"She has a knife."],[5105,5209,"Stay away from me!"],[5622,5684,"Jennifer!"],[5868,5935,"You're under arrest."],[6001,6106,"You're charged with kidnapping"],[6106,6210,"and attempted murder!"],[6210,6290,"You're safe now."],[6544,6623,"Ah!"],[6844,6894,"Watch out!"],[7102,7182,"—No! —Emma!"],[7182,7261,"No! No!"],[7369,7444,"No..."]],"59":[[383,529,"Emmy, it's gonna be okay!"],[529,617,"Emma, hang on!"],[1480,1644,"She needs a massive blood transfusion."],[1644,1864,"But she's got a rare O-negative blood type."],[1864,2047,"And the city blood banks don't have any!"],[2152,2235,"I'm O-negative!"],[2264,2367,"Can you take my blood?"],[2377,2456,"Great! Come with me."],[3123,3229,"As you are Emma's mother,"],[3229,3380,"we can't use your blood."],[3409,3487,"Wh—"],[3536,3595,"Her mother?"],[3828,3927,"What do you mean?"],[4012,4155,"Test results show that..."],[4179,4373,"the two of you are direct relatives."],[4617,4698,"You're her mother."],[4900,5019,"Emma is..."],[5050,5144,"my daughter?"],[5251,5329,"What?"],[5895,6000,"This is too much."],[6000,6078,"I..."],[6185,6368,"I finally find her after all this time,"],[6368,6495,"and I can't even save her."]],"60":[[66,133,"This..."],[237,312,"this is crazy."],[508,600,"Don't worry, Jennifer."],[675,846,"I won't let anything happen to Emma."],[1697,1755,"Urgent!"],[1818,1933,"We need blood donors,"],[1989,2152,"big rewards for anyone who helps!"],[2644,2723,"Thanks."],[3108,3233,"You're saving our girl."],[3319,3403,"Thank you."],[3482,3607,"Do whatever I can."],[4959,5093,"Your daughter's out of danger now."],[5121,5201,"Ah..."],[5259,5355,"Thank God!"],[5355,5438,"Thank you!"],[5551,5755,"You probably spent hundreds of thousands"],[5755,5885,"on blood donations..."]],"61":[[25,237,"Gave every last penny you had."],[258,358,"Don't worry."],[358,496,"I'm going to take care of you now."],[600,725,"Thank you"],[725,855,"for saving our daughter."],[1530,1630,"Every last penny?"],[1697,1768,"Sweetheart,"],[1822,1931,"I'm Paul Marshall,"],[1997,2118,"L.A.'s richest man."],[2389,2544,"Cracking jokes now?"],[2769,2902,"Well, let's go check on Emma."],[3812,3933,"She's waking up!"],[4562,4608,"Emma!"],[4738,4833,"My daughter!"],[4833,4978,"You're finally awake!"],[5046,5121,"Daughter?"],[5121,5205,"Um-hmm."],[5205,5313,"The transfusion tests..."],[5313,5417,"They proved it."],[5563,5655,"We're blood,"],[5655,5726,"you and I."],[5784,5930,"Wait... So,"],[6051,6143,"you're..."],[6143,6277,"You're really my mom?"],[6328,6394,"Um-hmm."],[6418,6539,"No doubt about it."],[6652,6698,"This?"],[6756,6878,"I gave it to you myself."],[7061,7156,"I can't believe it."],[7211,7278,"Mom!"],[7323,7450,"I finally found you!"],[8099,8266,"We're finally together as a family."],[8562,8612,"Wait."],[8704,8807,"It's not midnight yet!"],[8846,8892,"Dad,"],[8950,9067,"go get Mom's gifts."],[9121,9205,"It's true."],[9321,9367,"Go!"],[11027,11310,"You rented the Diamond Bachelor mansion?"],[11419,11547,"And all these presents?"]],"62":[[25,121,"It's your birthday, Jenn."],[200,392,"I've got one for every year that I missed with you."],[521,654,"You're too good to me."],[2056,2122,"Okay."],[2122,2348,"“Year one: a Diamond Bachelor mansion-"],[2348,2565,"welcome to this beautiful world.”"],[2623,2698,"Wait, what?!"],[2786,2865,"This place?!"],[2994,3040,"Yep,"],[3119,3203,"this mansion."],[3244,3332,"I tried to tell you."],[3403,3545,"I'm the richest guy in L.A."],[3616,3707,"Hold on."],[3849,3962,"All of this is..."],[3962,4070,"actually real?"],[4262,4358,"Every bit of it."],[4558,4929,"Okay, so, mansions worldwide, sports cars,"],[4929,5217,"a chopper, yachts, and freaking islands—"],[5217,5414,"I literally have it all."],[5463,5690,"What is left for you to top all of these?"],[5784,5910,"Open and find out."],[6277,6356,"Hahahaha."],[6418,6627,"Okay, so you've given me yourself..."],[6664,6765,"Hahahaha."],[6898,7048,"The PM Group?! Your company!"],[7157,7269,"Everything I've got—"],[7311,7403,"it's yours."],[7457,7582,"You've made me a better man."],[7582,7665,"That's..."],[7665,7778,"all I need to know."],[8145,8199,"Paul."],[8279,8404,"I should be thanking you."],[8483,8650,"You've shown me that..."],[8650,8779,"I'm worth loving again."],[8825,9034,"And given me the guts to love."],[9079,9200,"A real family,"],[9263,9455,"every wish I've ever had,"],[9455,9547,"you made it happen."],[9613,9704,"I love you."],[9763,9859,"I love you more,"],[9972,10030,"and I will..."],[10080,10147,"forever."]]}